{"tid":2508200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「黃圈未死！」 —— 五一懲罰祭！玩到十幾萬獎品？","createTime":"2021-04-28T14:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T07:22:13.000Z","uid":381081,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6ffdb2af5fe4fe812530ff963f95ccdda3db8c","tid":2508200,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:24:54.000Z","msg":"過去半年，香港的流行文化，從「樂壇已死」走到「樂壇不死」！<br />\n<br />\n靠的不只是藝人，而是<span class=\"orange\">香港人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n過往這幾個月，每逢提到黃店 / 黃色經濟圈，聽到的似乎都是壞消息：有黃店再度告急，才能重見一兩天的人潮；有些黃店沒有選擇告急，唯有選擇默默結業。在疫情與政府打壓下，許多小店苦苦堅持，黃色經濟圈似乎失去了昔日的活力與力量。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n香港樂壇，只要有香港人聽就永遠不死！<br />\n<br />\n同樣，黃圈有香港人撐就永遠不死！<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n今次的五一懲罰祭，又有新玩法（留意我地個Page），而亦<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">獎品總值更高達六位數字</span></span>！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年的五一懲罰祭，將會進一步延長至五月九日，橫跨兩個週末，希望能夠同時透過母親節的效應，為黃店帶來更多營業額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣Template👉 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2R3vj15\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2R3vj15&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzcwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=e9f0577c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2R3vj15</a><br />\n（歡迎已收到確認信息的商戶下載使用）<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n登記表格<br />\n實體商戶👉 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/51week1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F51week1&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzcwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=f3cb4814\" target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/51week1</a><br />\n網店/非實體商戶👉 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/51week2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F51week2&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzcwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=b9523f60\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/51week2</a><br />\n懲罰MEE👉 <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/PunishC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2FPunishC&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzcwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=406cdcd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/PunishC</a>"},{"pid":"74ab817914a116ccc43d68324c839d855ffcaaca","tid":2508200,"uid":381081,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWPBBywCLYKSnodq4kZptuuwHqf75D2gnsDfx9QU28EaK?filename=k62pZYk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk62pZYk.jpg&h=cab195c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"beefe9cd8021be7e448a2fcb66e26f368ccbe5ca","tid":2508200,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168e82c1a7a40a1100e92836657d5c1da1dcc031","tid":2508200,"uid":39855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:27:11.000Z","msg":"大家上呀！"},{"pid":"46e2859c3711d1bbed480cc0d861fa10d006d599","tid":2508200,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b094e863498ba144330a0b83478235c974f72174","tid":2508200,"uid":159271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"push 留名"},{"pid":"5659070e1b804c11106f0b5941e2b661be4c7091","tid":2508200,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:28:09.000Z","msg":"你隻app去左邊？"},{"pid":"e4a092e1fac22cb0d8669441e1b356a546635b20","tid":2508200,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3e6948a791c7c5764c1b152b26c240c9f6523b","tid":2508200,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0