ore":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一年一度水魚圈 唔知有無Marco"},{"pid":"2fc6a50de902fa64e9bc82a0c98e2e15b9754905","tid":2508200,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"龍門嘅背景同食物質素雖然受到多方面嘅質疑，但絕不能無視佢當日推動黃圈嘅角色<br />\n<br />\n於運動期間，龍門係頭幾間黃店出現排隊幫襯嘅現象，唔多唔少為「懲罰」set 了一個benchmark <br />\n<br />\n但可惜，老細逆市擴充嘅算盤打唔響。<br />\n<br />\n半年內加開左4間分店，高峰期一共有8間分店<br />\n<br />\nMee非常感激老細喺黃圈早期落力推動，但全港18區都有唔少立場堅定而且有一定食物水準嘅黃店，絕對有能力為當區嘅同路人服務！無需老細天價租舖擴充<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你點睇 「小店」渣哥嘅食物質素？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXy5M5nGut2k9kfChisrqLfoD2Z2AspquTqrPspKnnaVt?filename=Rsn5KyB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRsn5KyB.png&h=20c4b7bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUsBAkvu76wCEkiQkBMTf4VFruybsECJv5gvhYrdurGMZ?filename=6wzDj6X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wzDj6X.png&h=09710f72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWmwiH1cUxcErxUGpFHGBhrwnubRNPWU2KiAuFXQDNQUp?filename=N5BBRdD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5BBRdD.jpg&h=860f8b1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8c9154bdad0b47c8b78bd769b43863b82e3d54e","tid":2508200,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b06081619af986858b94cbdcb955a6698688f6e","tid":2508200,"uid":374209,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一年一度水魚圈 唔知有無Marco"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" 